5105  code()->GetInstructionBlock(gap_index)->IsDeferred());
5106 
5107  ParallelMove* move =
5108  code()->InstructionAt(gap_index)->GetOrCreateParallelMove(
5109  gap_pos, code_zone());
5110  if (!delay_insertion) {
5111  move->AddMove(prev_operand, cur_operand);
5112  } else {
5113  delayed_insertion_map.insert(
5114  std::make_pair(std::make_pair(move, prev_operand), cur_operand));
5115  }
5116  }
5117  }
5118  if (delayed_insertion_map.empty()) return;
5119  // Insert all the moves which should occur after the stored move.
5120  ZoneVector<MoveOperands*> to_insert(local_zone);
5121  ZoneVector<MoveOperands*> to_eliminate(local_zone);
5122  to_insert.reserve(4);
5123  to_eliminate.reserve(4);
5124  ParallelMove* moves = delayed_insertion_map.begin()->first.first;
5125  for (auto it = delayed_insertion_map.begin();; ++it) {
5126  bool done = it == delayed_insertion_map.end();
5127  if (done || it->first.first != moves) {
5128  // Commit the MoveOperands for current ParallelMove.
5129  for (MoveOperands* move : to_eliminate) {
5130  move->Eliminate();
5131  }
5132  for (MoveOperands* move : to_insert) {
5133  moves->push_back(move);
5134  }
5135  if (done) break;
5136  // Reset state.
5137  to_eliminate.clear();
5138  to_insert.clear();
5139  moves = it->first.first;
5140  }
5141  // Gather all MoveOperands for a single ParallelMove.
5142  MoveOperands* move =
5143  code_zone()->New<MoveOperands>(it->first.second, it->second);
5144  moves->PrepareInsertAfter(move, &to_eliminate);
5145  to_insert.push_back(move);
5146  }
5147 }
5148 
5149 void LiveRangeConnector::CommitSpillsInDeferredBlocks(TopLevelLiveRange* range,
5150  Zone* temp_zone) {
5151  DCHECK(range->IsSpilledOnlyInDeferredBlocks(data()));
5152  DCHECK(!range->spilled());
5153 
5154  InstructionSequence* code = data()->code();
5155  InstructionOperand spill_operand = range->GetSpillRangeOperand();
5156 
5157  TRACE("Live Range %d will be spilled only in deferred blocks.\n",
5158  range->vreg());
5159  // If we have ranges that aren't spilled but require the operand on the stack,
5160  // make sure we insert the spill.
5161  for (const LiveRange* child = range; child != nullptr;
5162  child = child->next()) {
5163  for (const UsePosition* pos : child->positions()) {
5164  if (pos->type() != UsePositionType::kRequiresSlot && !child->spilled())
5165  continue;
5166  range->AddBlockRequiringSpillOperand(
5167  code->GetInstructionBlock(pos->pos().ToInstructionIndex())
5168  ->rpo_number(),
5169  data());
5170  }
5171  }
5172 
5173  ZoneQueue<int> worklist(temp_zone);
5174 
5175  for (int block_id : *range->GetListOfBlocksRequiringSpillOperands(data())) {
5176  worklist.push(block_id);
5177  }
5178 
5179  ZoneSet<std::pair<RpoNumber, int>> done_moves(temp_zone);
5180  // Seek the deferred blocks that dominate locations requiring spill operands,
5181  // and spill there. We only need to spill at the start of such blocks.
5182  SparseBitVector done_blocks(temp_zone);
5183  while (!worklist.empty()) {
5184  int block_id = worklist.front();
5185  worklist.pop();
5186  if (done_blocks.Contains(block_id)) continue;
5187  done_blocks.Add(block_id);
5188  InstructionBlock* spill_block =
5189  code->InstructionBlockAt(RpoNumber::FromInt(block_id));
5190 
5191  for (const RpoNumber& pred : spill_block->predecessors()) {
5192  const InstructionBlock* pred_block = code->InstructionBlockAt(pred);
5193 
5194  if (pred_block->IsDeferred()) {
5195  worklist.push(pred_block->rpo_number().ToInt());
5196  } else {
5197  LifetimePosition pred_end =
5198  LifetimePosition::InstructionFromInstructionIndex(
5199  pred_block->last_instruction_index());
5200 
5201  LiveRange* child_range = range->GetChildCovers(pred_end);
5202  DCHECK_NOT_NULL(child_range);
5203 
5204  InstructionOperand pred_op = child_range->GetAssignedOperand();
5205 
5206  RpoNumber spill_block_number = spill_block->rpo_number();
5207  if (done_moves.find(std::make_pair(
5208  spill_block_number, range->vreg())) == done_moves.end()) {
5209  TRACE("Spilling deferred spill for range %d at B%d\n", range->vreg(),
5210  spill_block_number.ToInt());
5211  data()->AddGapMove(spill_block->first_instruction_index(),
5212  Instruction::GapPosition::START, pred_op,
5213  spill_operand);
5214  done_moves.insert(std::make_pair(spill_block_number, range->vreg()));
5215  spill_block->mark_needs_frame();
5216  }
5217  }
5218  }
5219  }
5220 }
5221 
5222 #undef TRACE
